Text: "Yes its true who tells that Istanbul is a Magic country ,l spent my days in\
  \ \u015Ei\u015Fli where l found a beautiful places .every day l Walked in those\
  \ quiet streets then l went to play football on its Green field .in the evenning\
  \ l spent my time in front of the black seas and posphours views .in the cold days\
  \ l spent most of my time skating on the high mountain peaks .its dishes l never\
  \ forgot its so delicious .really \u0130stanbul is a paradise .l love this country..."
